sequenceDiagram
    participant MR as model_runner
    participant ADP as Adapter
    participant LP as LogitsProc
    participant K as Kernels

    MR->>ADP: call with logits
    ADP->>ADP: build mapping ctx
    ADP->>LP: apply

    alt default mode
        LP->>K: logit bias
        LP->>K: penalties
        LP->>K: bad words
        LP->>K: temperature
        LP->>K: min p
        LP->>K: topk and topp
    else skip mode
        LP->>LP: check and warn
        Note over LP: no kernel launches
    end

    LP-->>ADP: processed logits
    ADP->>K: gumbel sample
    K-->>ADP: sampled ids
    ADP->>K: compute logprobs
    K-->>ADP: logprobs tensors
    ADP-->>MR: SamplerOutput
